Comment: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Comment: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.95,orig,,0,0,0,,You could smell it from here?
Comment: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.85,orig,,0,0,0,,What made you say that?
Comment: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Comment: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.90,orig,,0,0,0,,I see why you come here so much.
Comment: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.70,orig,,0,0,0,,I'm up, I'm awake...
Comment: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.05,orig,,0,0,0,,You're fine here on the deck.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.35,orig,,0,0,0,,What will we do?
Comment: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.20,orig,,0,0,0,,I guess, boring.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.85,orig,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Comment: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.00,orig,,0,0,0,,I need a moment.
Comment: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.35,orig,,0,0,0,,That would be difficult and painful.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.20,orig,,0,0,0,,...or in the future.
Comment: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.11,orig,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect you to.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.20,orig,,0,0,0,,I decided to learn the sneak attack, "Spider," and paid forty silvers for it.
Comment: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.10,orig,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.50,orig,,0,0,0,,If you were, you could say "goodbye" to your neck and body.
Comment: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.35,orig,,0,0,0,,I'll die! I'm not kidding!
Comment: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.55,orig,,0,0,0,,What a drab man you are.
Comment: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Yes, dull!
Comment: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:50.20,orig,,0,0,0,,It's not once a day, but I do see it pretty often—

Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:39.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:44.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:02.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:08.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:12.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:22.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:28.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:35.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:41.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:49.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,After talking it over, we all decided to take the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,We had a lot going on until yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and it feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,...a good time to take, like, a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:30.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,But, I wonder what this strange feeling is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:33.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,What do I usually do on days off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A day off, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I actually get a break, I feel a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta-kun went out early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those people who get up\Nearlier when they don't have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This bread's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the timing down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to change the temperature in between...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's hard with logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about cooking duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I don't appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to be hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Ranta go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He had his fishing rod with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yume and Shihoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen them all morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're still in their room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,They probably stayed up late...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,...since Shihoru was crying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,She and Yume probably talked about Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Moguzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of taking my armor in to get fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It got pretty damaged in our last fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My weapon was beat up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I left it to get sharpened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to go pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you usually do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We hardly get days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.85,fix,,0,0,0,,Me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all meeting at Shelly's Tavern in the evening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, I didn't know you were up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You... like birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... it's just become a habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Moguzo baked this new bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It smelled good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Even from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We all watched the sunset from here, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to continue working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.85,fix,,0,0,0,,Uh, what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunrise is beautiful from here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.55,fix,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.90,fix,,0,0,0,,That's why you come here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, Shihoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.35,fix,,0,0,0,,I'm up, I'm awake...  awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lodging for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here since I left the Volunteer Soldier lodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so I shouldn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.10,fix,,0,0,0,,On the terrace is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you plan to leave your lodging...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe I will tell Yume and Shihoru about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be happy to hear about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're probably pretty used to our lodgings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's likely that we'll leave eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of memories... in those lodgings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,When Merry stayed at those dingy lodgings, she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,...probably... with her original party-mates...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,...with the comrades... who are no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? In Damuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was super ferocious, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lin-gob or something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I only understood the ferocious part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There were some newcomers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kie-roos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kie-roos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, rookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they Volunteer Soldier trainees?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kie-roo ty-par got into some trouble in Damuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bad, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure the goblins we defeated were from the new city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Their equipment and the way they\Nmoved was completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we defeated them—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad lin-gobs from the new city came\Nand started angrily patrolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we supposed to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them laying flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a pancake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At least while they're piping hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the gobs making trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they are. But the problem is that it's in Damuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So what're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.35,fix,,0,0,0,,"What?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I haven't thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were planning on going to Damuro tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go to Damuro tomorrow and don't earn anything,\Nyou better take responsibility for it, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you better show you mean it by paying up your portion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we earn nothing, my portion is also nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we change our hunting grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, sorry, I was talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro! You say some pretty good things once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I mean once in a {\i1}long{\i0} while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Tetra Pods in the Cyrene Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a bounty of thirty golds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "Tetra Pods" but "Death Spots" from the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, we'll need to change\Nour hunting grounds for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know anything about other places,\Nso I was wondering where we could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take extra precautions to avoid Death Spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And always being in the same area can get a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.20,fix,,0,0,0,,I guess, it feels boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We fall into a routine and make\Ncareless mistakes because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it'd be good for us to have some\Nexcitement or be under pressure once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...to go to the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad to do the same thing every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been in fewer dangerous situations lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I've been able to save money a little at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay with how it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just that we can't go to Damuro right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's our only choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if we change our prey,\Nit'll be a nice change of pace, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.50,fix,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.00,fix,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,If we go to the Cyrene Mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:25.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry will have to step foot in the place...\Nwhere she lost her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.55,fix_it,,0,0,0,,That would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.40,fix_it,,0,0,0,,And very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:39.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,We actually haven't been near the place\Nwhere Manato breathed his last either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's to the point that I wish I could forget such a place exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Cyrene Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can be calm in the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.20,fix,,0,0,0,,...and probably... never will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.10,fix,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have to overcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I {\i1}want{\i0} to overcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I feel like I won't be able to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I know I can't overcome it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to have help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd want it to be you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd make me happy if I could go with you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you called me your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably just causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'd think of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.55,fix,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe these are tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel stupid right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine just like that, Haru{Hal}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:47.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,We decided to be fully prepared before facing the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,We prepared our equipment and skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:57.25,fix_it,,0,0,0,,I decided to pay forty silvers and\Nlearn the sneak attack, "Spider."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started, Old Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.10,fix,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten a little stiff since the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure only things that are hanging get stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm not stiff th—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.50,fix,,0,0,0,,If you were, your neck could say "goodbye" to your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have my dagger, removing your\Nneck vertebrae wouldn't be bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First step for you is to fully experience my Spider...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...until you're vomiting blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There have only been a few people\Nwho have died from my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There were people who actually died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use if you can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to train even when you're resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit-ups, sit-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you rather do some\Ntraining on how to withstand torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.35,fix,,0,0,0,,I'll die! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we just make small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I— I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do as you're told, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Small... talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind a little story, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.55,fix,,0,0,0,,What a boring guy{man} you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you can't get any girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... deny that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have girls in your party, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Make one of them yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, having all of them would be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... I'd rather not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at least interested in one of them, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You just pictured someone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, teacher...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something I wanted to... ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with women, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho, you're changing the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the energy to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, do not get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get the wrong idea, because\NI have absolutely no idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How dull can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you are an old cat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dull?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Dull!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Although your intuition isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's gained a lot of experience will\Nsee that streak of light at least once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:50.20,fix,,0,0,0,,In my case... it's not once a day... but I do see it pretty often—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not unheard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It differs greatly from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can see just by concentrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To see it with more certainty,\Nyou need to improve your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your physical strength, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have enough breath to say you don't\Nhave energy, I haven't pushed you far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a normal mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Long ago, the Cyrene Mine was developed\Nwhen the Arabikia Kingdom of humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,...decided they wanted to control the frontier lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:55.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Under the command of No Life King, a party of kobolds\Nousted the humans and seized the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:59.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,The kobolds have been living in the mine since.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:55.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:03.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:13.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:19.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:33.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
